{"title":"今日小货郎（图片）","authors":["王东","叶伴"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":10,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日小货郎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小呀么小货郎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背起那货物上市场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕太阳晒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕风雨狂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只怕生意不兴旺哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挣不够钱，无颜见爹娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小呀么小儿郎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快背起书包上学堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫受小利诱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫怕歪风狂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只怕又成新文盲哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有学问，无颜是爹娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本报记者　王东摄于广西罗城仫佬族自治县"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶伴配诗"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}